flowchart TD
    A[Add or update model for search] --> B[Include BetterTogether::Searchable]
    B --> C[Implement as_indexed_json with normalized plain text]
    C --> D{Need native pg_search ranking?}
    D -- No --> E[Call searchable with no pg_search config]
    E --> F[Model is searchable through PgSearch adapter fallback]
    D -- Yes --> G[Call searchable pg_search: {...}]
    G --> H[Put only real DB columns in against:]
    H --> I[Let Searchable auto-merge translations]
    I --> J{Model has special SQL-backed associations worth ranking?}
    J -- No --> K[Use shared translation associations only]
    J -- Yes --> L[Add supported associated_against entries]
    K --> M[Add model to Search::Registry via concern]
    L --> M
    F --> M
    M --> N[Model can surface in database and pg_search modes]
    C --> O[Ensure ES payload includes the same user-meaningful content]
    O --> P[Model can surface in Elasticsearch mode]
    N --> Q[Add targeted backend specs]
    P --> Q
